ing: 1 (16 ounce) package shredded Monterey Jack cheese
2 (4 ounce) cans sliced black olives, drained
4 (4.5 ounce) cans diced green chiles, drained
des: "Thanks to my friend Tina for this recipe. It's so good because it's so different.  If you like corn, green onions and tomatoes, you'll love it!"
ins: In a 2 quart bowl or larger, combine the Monterey Jack cheese, black olives, tomatoes, chilies, onions and corn. Pour in salad dressing, and stir to coat. Dressing may be adjusted to suit your taste.
